It contains 19 classified findings across implementation divergences, ambiguous spec points, stale spec/API notes, missing tests, and no-discrepancy confirmations. Key discrepancies include dry-run creating `runtime/transitions.log`, journal lines recording `build→build` style invocation lifecycle instead of actual transitions, callback-only runs bypassing TUI/journal events, missing `notify` log tailing, incomplete grid layout behavior, and timeout outcome misclassification.

